             was indicted for <rs id="t18291029-193-off1083" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18291029-193-off1083" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18291029-193-off1083" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18291029-193-cd1084" type="crimeDate">11th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18291029-193-off1083 t18291029-193-cd1084"></join>, seven 20l., twenty 10l., six 5l., one 55l., and one 65l. promissory notes, the property of 
                     <persName id="t18291029-193-victim1574" type="victimName">
                        Vincent 
                        Stuckey
                     <interp inst="t18291029-193-victim1574" type="surname" value="Stuckey"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18291029-193-victim1574" type="given" value="Vincent"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18291029-193-victim1574" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                   and others, in the dwelling-house of 
